            <lg xml:id="TK964">
<l>talaiyi ṉiḻinta mayiraṉaiyar māntar </l>
<l>nilaiyi ṉiḻintak kaṭai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>They who have fallen from their (high) position are like the hair which has fallen from the head.</l>
